title: VA - Now THATS What Beolab Calls Music (2013) MP3VBR Beolab1700
description:
---------------------------------------------------------------------

If hip hop, X Idol or Rap (Really? Rap, Damn) is your thing then move along there really is nothing to see here.
If you're intrested in discovering a new band, song or simply something a bit different to what you would usually listen to then maybe
just maybe this might be right for you.

As a regular uploader over many sites I often get comments or requests for 'other bands that sound like' or 'Your taste in music is impeccable!'
( Which its not, its just my taste and everybody's is different ) So I decided to put this, ahem, imaginatively titled little collection together in an attepmt
to showcase some of the lesser known talent out there interspersed with some more recognisable names to give it context, so if you do spot a song or band you do
know chances are you're gonna like at least a few more songs on here. Is this indulgent on my part? without a doubt, LOL.

So kick back, open a Bottle of Jack Daniel's or roll a big one, whatever your persuasion and enjoy. Beolab.
